The paper discusses the use of AI algorithms in a collaborative image guessing game, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HCI). The game involves visual question answering (VQA), which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also evaluates the impact of AI explanations on human performance, which is a topic within the field of machine learning (cs.LG) and specifically, explainable AI (cs.AI).
